&lt;p&gt;An exciting opportunity has risen for an experience Senior Project Manager to be responsible for delivery of the implementation of a consolidated Laboratory Information Management System (LIMS) across Sherwood Forest Hospitals (SFH) in conjunction with Nottingham University Hospitals (NUH).&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The post holder will work in the NUH Project Manager to implement a LIMS across the two trusts. The post holder will also work in partnership with Nottingham Health Informatics Service (NHIS), to ensure the Business Case and allocated resources are aligned.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Donna Oakes Job title Deputy Divisional General Manager for Diagnostics and Outpatients Email address donna.oakes@nhs.net Telephone number 07791694961&lt;/p&gt;
